OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782800290
OL,3,CSupreme court rejects Trump's bid to
OL,4,Cappeal E. Jean Carroll sex abuse case
OL,6,FTrump called the decision to pass on
OL,7,Fthe Carroll case "surprising" in a
OL,8,Fsocial media post, and he said he
OL,9,Fwould continue to fight the defamation
OL,10,Fclaims.
OL,12,FTrump's lawyers had argued that
OL,13,Fallegations leading to the verdict
OL,14,Fwere propped up by "highly
OL,15,Finflammatory" evidentiary rulings,
OL,16,Fincluding those that allowed the
OL,17,Ftestimony of two other women who
OL,18,Faccused Trump of sexual abuse decades
OL,19,Fago. Trump has denied all three
OL,20,Fwomen's allegations.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
