OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782800290
OL,3,CSupreme court rejects Trump's bid to
OL,4,Cappeal E. Jean Carroll sex abuse case
OL,6,FCarroll's lawyers had urged the
OL,7,Fjustices to pass on the case. They
OL,8,Fargued that the women's testimony was
OL,9,Frelevant because the allegations were
OL,10,Fsimilar and that Judge Lewis Kaplan's
OL,11,Fdecisions were in line with others
OL,12,Faround the country.
OL,14,F"This question is not worthy of
OL,15,Freview," wrote attorney Roberta
OL,16,FKaplan, who is not related to the
OL,17,Fjudge.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
