OL,3,CSupreme court rejects Trump's bid to
OL,4,Cappeal E. Jean Carroll sex abuse case
OL,6,FMonday's decision affirms the jury's
OL,7,Fverdict will stand, she said in a
OL,8,Fstatement Monday. "His multiple
OL,9,Fefforts to appeal that verdict have
OL,10,Fall failed and today's ruling ends his
OL,11,Fquest to avoid accountability for his
OL,12,Factions," she said.
