OL,3,CSupreme court rejects Trump's bid to
OL,4,Cappeal E. Jean Carroll sex abuse case
OL,6,FCarroll, a longtime advice columnist
OL,7,Fand former TV talk show host,
OL,8,Ftestified at a 2023 trial that Trump
OL,9,Fturned a friendly encounter in spring
OL,10,F1996 into a violent attack in the
OL,11,Fdressing room at Bergdorf Goodman, a
OL,12,Fluxury retailer across the street from
OL,13,FTrump Tower in Manhattan.
OL,15,FThe jury also found Trump liable for
OL,16,Fdefaming Carroll when he denied her
OL,17,Fallegation in 2022.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
