OL,3,CSupreme court rejects Trump's bid to
OL,4,Cappeal E. Jean Carroll sex abuse case
OL,6,FTrump has successfully fended off
OL,7,Fother hefty court judgments, including
OL,8,Fa New York civil fraud penalty of over
OL,9,F$500 million thrown out by a New York
OL,10,Fappeals court. The Supreme Court also
OL,11,Fgranted him broad immunity from
OL,12,Fcriminal prosecution in 2024, though
OL,13,Fit later narrowly rejected his bid to
OL,14,Fhalt sentencing in his New York hush
OL,15,Fmoney case.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
